**- IDE Commands**
_____________________________
ide.open // Open a file
ide.exit // Exit environment
ide.clear // Clear Console
ide.help // Redirect to here

_____________________________

**- FLS Program Commands** 
_____________________________
Text.Write("Hello World!")

Displays the text written in the console
Program.Exit("exemple.exe")

Close a program.
Program.Execute("exemple.exe")

Execute a program.
Time.Pause("1000")

Wait
System.Power=Shutdown

Shutdown Operating System.
System.Power=Reboot

Reboot Operating System.
Folder.Create("C:\Users\username\Desktop\folder")

Create a folder
Folder.Delete("C:\Users\username\Desktop\folder")

Delete a folder
File.Create("C:\Users\username\Desktop\text.txt")

Create a file
File.Delete("C:\Users\username\Desktop\text.txt")

Shutdown PC
System.Power=Shutdown

Restart PC
System.Power=Reboot

Set Text Color
Color.Set=Red
Color.Set=Green
Color.Set=Blue
Color.Set=White
Color.Set=Yellow
Color.Set=Black
Color.Set=Gray
Color.Set=DarkRed
